text: It has a nice look on the outside, it has a playground near the flats, it has a bbq pit, a garden for people living on the first floor. Design nice, the inside was also nice so 4 stars. I do have some nice pictures when I reach home. Hope you like it(sorry if I put the camera to low)
I thought is condominium but is not lol. Anyway very nice design with balcony facing bedok village. Schools, coffeeshops, shops, vus stops to MRT, parks are nearby for your daily needs.
Very nice environment but house a little too small for a big family... If u r just a couple then space is not a worry...
